summary:
I'm an enthusiastic Software Developer with many years of experience working for different industries.
I enjoy developing meaningful products as a result of a close collaboration with my stakeholders.

One of the biggest achievements in my career (and in my life) so far has been finding a job that would sponsor me and my family to move to the EU. 

Besides work, wellness is a key factor of motivation for me, as well as a good workplace culture. 
In my spare time I enjoy spending time with my family, playing sports and discovering new places.
